text: Þis aren þe landmæres into Haddedune.
Erest of erningestrete into Sumerlededic, and of þare dic into billingbroc.
Andlang broces, and of þan broce into þe mære.
Norð of þan mære andlong Weyes into aldandic.
East andlang dices into ellenstyb and on þa stræte.
And suð andlang stræte þat it comeð foren ongean sumerlededic þer it ær bigan þat fiue hiða land mære.
